"""
        Test that the client can check an object.
        """
result = {'unique_identifier': '1', 'result_status': enums.ResultStatus.SUCCESS
    }
client = ProxyKmipClient()
client.open()
client.proxy.check.return_value = result
checked_id = client.check(uid='1', usage_limits_count=100,
    cryptographic_usage_mask=[enums.CryptographicUsageMask.ENCRYPT, enums.
    CryptographicUsageMask.DECRYPT], lease_time=10000)
self.assertEqual('1', checked_id)
mock.patch('kmip.pie.client.KMIPProxy', mock.MagicMock(spec_set=KMIPProxy))
